    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/553b0722cb2ec56f613ef3bac2955ac8.poster.avif?t=1763843721\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/553b0722cb2ec56f613ef3bac2955ac8.webm?t=1763843721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/553b0722cb2ec56f613ef3bac2955ac8.mp4?t=1763843721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decide Who Boards the Plane</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customer satisfaction is what it's all about, but some passengers just aren't worth the hassle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If someone looks like a troublemaker, feel free to reject them at boarding and luxuriate in their absence during the flight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/a5d9931087fc1acf7855fbed6a5ce5aa.poster.avif?t=1763843721\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/a5d9931087fc1acf7855fbed6a5ce5aa.webm?t=1763843721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/a5d9931087fc1acf7855fbed6a5ce5aa.mp4?t=1763843721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the Joys of Airborne Customer Service</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anticipate your passengers' needs, keep them comfortable, and strive to provide a survivable flight for all paying customers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/29677cd83d6701f7f2991d175aa62964.poster.avif?t=1763843721\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/29677cd83d6701f7f2991d175aa62964.webm?t=1763843721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/29677cd83d6701f7f2991d175aa62964.mp4?t=1763843721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unravel the Occult Ritual</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Malevolent entities are threatening the lives of everyone on board. In order to survive, you must uncover hidden evils and disrupt their foul magicks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/3477231582a3085181ef9bd10c4dcd60.poster.avif?t=1763843721\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/3477231582a3085181ef9bd10c4dcd60.webm?t=1763843721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/3477231582a3085181ef9bd10c4dcd60.mp4?t=1763843721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Save(?) Innocent(?) Souls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everyone on board is relying on you to rescue them from eternal suffering, whether they know it or not.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to see past the superficial eccentricities of your passengers, save whoever you think is human, and escape the doppelgängers and demons clothed in deceptive flesh. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/fecc531881ee5dfb0ab8091049918bb7.poster.avif?t=1763843721\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/fecc531881ee5dfb0ab8091049918bb7.webm?t=1763843721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310570/extras/fecc531881ee5dfb0ab8091049918bb7.mp4?t=1763843721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
